high_descs: Turn around, and go forward to the sink.
Pick up the potato on the counter to the left of the sink.
Turn around, and go forward until you reach the fridge then turn left.
Open the fridge, potato inside and chill it, then take it out.
Turn left and go forward toward the counter, then turn right at the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the potato inside and close it.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold potato in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around, and walk to the sink.
Pick up the avocado from the sink.
Turn around, walk across the room, then turn left, and walk forward to you hit the fridge.
Open the fridge, place the avocado inside, wait three seconds, then open the door and remove the avocado.
Turn left, walk forward, then turn right to face the microwave.
Place the avocado in the microwave and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold avocado in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right walk straight to left side of the counter beside the sink
Pick up the potato beside the bread on the counter
Turn right walk forward then face the fridge on your left
Open fridge then put in and out the potato then close the fridge
Turn left walk forward then turn right
Open the microwave and put in the potato
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled potato in the microwave
